window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Xeraphine Nora</b></p> <p>For a decade, revenge has consumed my every waking thought. My sole desire? To mete out even a fraction of the suffering inflicted upon me by those five individuals. They believed they could silence me forever, burying me alive and leaving me for dead. Little did they know, it takes more than mundane means to kill a demon. I’m coming for you all, my sweets.</p> <p><b>Kairhyse Monroe</b></p> <p>Finding the demon responsible for these murders is what brought me to her, but my obsession is what keeps me chasing. Oh, Xeraphine, if you believe you’ll find freedom from my grasp, you are truly mistaken. I’m coming for you, my little demon.</p> <p>Please check the TW (available on the authors website: mlburnsauthor.com).</p>"; 
